<L>__{exterior main street macreedy}
<A>__{headed towards doc's establishment. the building, which serves doc as home, office and laboratory, has centered on a pane of glass: t.r. velie, jr. undertaker and veterinary and in the lower right hand corner:}
<B>__{assayer notary public}
<A>__{a few of the peeled gold and black letters are completely missing. the building is separated from the structure next to it by an alleyway. filling the narrow passage is hector david, his long massive body wedged against the wall like an unkempt monument. his little pig eyes meet macreedy's. hector spits in the dust with bland insolence.}
